snippet.title: Lan Party Adventures - World Premiere Reveal Trailer | FGS LIVE FROM GDC
snippet.description:
The world premiere reveal trailer for Lan Party Adventures, a new thrilling, nostalgic mystery game where the player builds LAN parties while trying to locate their missing friend. Lan Party Adventures is now available to wishlist on Steam. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #gdc #lanpartyadventures

Future Publishing uses the Epidemic Sound Library and Adobe Creative Cloud Generative AI features
